  <h1>Was ist Docker?</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>Von Coldwast</span><span>Aktualisiert am 19. Juni 2026</span><span>8 Min. Lesezeit</span><span class="tag">#docker</span><span class="tag">#containers</span><span class="tag">#devops</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
